<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Mitti Scan OTP Verification</title>

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fb;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #27b755;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .header-icon {
      font-size: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 30px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .otp-box {
      background-color: #f6fdf8;
      border: 2px dashed #27b755;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .otp {
      font-size: 34px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 8px;
      color: #1f9645;
    }

    .info {
      color: #555555;
      font-size: 15px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .warning {
      margin-top: 25px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #888888;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #1e293b;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #27b755;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="container">

    <div class="header">
      <span class="header-icon">🌱</span>
      <h1>Mitti Scan</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">

      <div class="greeting">
        Hello {{name}},
      </div>

      <p>Your verification code to access your farm dashboard is:</p>

      <div class="otp-box">
        <div class="otp">{{otp}}</div>
      </div>

      <p class="info">
        This code is valid for <strong>5 minutes</strong>.
      </p>

      <p class="warning">
        Please do not share this code with anyone. If you did not request to log in to Mitti Scan, you can safely ignore this email.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Need help? Contact <a href="mailto:support@mittiscan.in">support@mittiscan.in</a></p>
      <p>&copy; 2026 Mitti Scan. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>